About SAMAutoTester:

This is an app developed to test the sam service functionalities


Once the SAMAutoTester toggle button is enabled, it automatically connects & registers to the SAM service with unsolicited callback

There are two options/test modes available in the test app
i) Individual Functionality Test
ii) Automated Functionality Test

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Individual Functionality Test:

This option displays the ui to verify each functionlity provided by sam service
i) getCardState
ii) getCardATR
iii) getSlotMapping
iv) streamApdu
v) switchSlot
vi) cardPowerUp
vii) cardPowerDown


Input:
Input is entered in the provided edit text for corresponding functionalities


Output:
Synchronous messages are displayed as text message in the app UI
Async responses are shown as a toast messages

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Automated Functionality Test:

Input:
Input file 'input_sam.txt' should be placed in the 'ExternalStorageDirectory' i.e. /storage/emulated/0 on the phone
The input file format is described in the SAMPLE_INPUT file

Output:
Output file 'output_sam.txt' is generated in the same location(/storage/emulated/0) once the test execution is completed.


